capturedLogs.message: 🚀 Starting comprehensive CutProcessorMigrated debug test for M1002.nc
- Old CutProcessor: Monolithic, direct CSG operations
- New CutProcessorMigrated: Modular architecture with adapters
* Handler not found for END_CUT type

criticalIssues: 25 cuts have bounds outside geometry - may not be visible

recommendations: Verify CutProcessorMigrated is being used by FeatureProcessorFactory
Check if cut handlers are registered for END_CUT feature type
Ensure CSG operations are not failing silently
Validate that userData.cuts is being populated correctly
Check FeatureOutlineRenderer is reading userData.cuts properly
Verify face mapping for AK blocks (front/back/top/bottom faces)
Test with simpler cut geometries first to isolate the issue
Enable verbose logging in CutProcessorMigrated constructor
Check if three-bvh-csg library is properly imported and working
Verify geometry vertices count changes after CSG operations
